OL,3,CWater company fine reduced by over 90%
OL,5,FThe charges related to self-monitoring
OL,6,Fdata submitted by Welsh Water to
OL,7,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) as part
OL,8,Fof its 2020 and 2021 annual reports.
OL,10,FSince 2010, water companies have been
OL,11,Frequired to carry out self-monitoring
OL,12,Fof effluent discharges from sewage and
OL,13,Fwater treatment works.
OL,15,FWelsh Water attributed the issues to a
OL,16,Fcombination of factors, including an
OL,17,Finternal restructure of its sampling
OL,18,Fteam, IT-related scheduling problems,
OL,19,Fand the operational challenges posed
OL,20,Fby the Covid-19 pandemic.
