OL,3,CWater company fine reduced by over 90%
OL,5,FOn Friday, 17 October, a Welsh Water
OL,6,Fspokesperson said: "We are pleased our
OL,7,Fappeal against the level of fine was
OL,8,Fsuccessful.
OL,10,F"There was no identified environmental
OL,11,Fharm associated with this case, and
OL,12,Fthe monitoring failures represented a
OL,13,Fvery small proportion (around 1%) of a
OL,14,Fprogramme involving tens of thousands
OL,15,Fof submissions each year.
