OL,3,CWater company fine reduced by over 90%
OL,5,FUpon receiving the company's 2020
OL,6,Freport, NRW officers expressed concern
OL,7,Fthat the quality of submitted data had
OL,8,F"noticeably deteriorated" compared to
OL,9,Fprevious years, with over 600 breaches
OL,10,Frecorded.
OL,12,FAlthough the 2021 report showed
OL,13,Fsignificant improvement, a number of
OL,14,Fnon-compliances were still identified.
OL,16,FNRW said that due to missing samples
OL,17,Fand data in 2020, they were unable to
OL,18,Ffully assess or respond to any
OL,19,Fpotential environmental impacts.
