OL,5,FIn response, Welsh Water stated: "A
OL,6,Fcombination of factors impacted our
OL,7,Fwork during 2020-21 that included the
OL,8,FCovid-19 pandemic. Despite this we met
OL,9,Four monitoring requirements, which
OL,10,Finvolve more than 18,000 tests per
OL,11,Fyear, 98.95% of the time in 2020 and
OL,12,F99.45% in 2021.
OL,14,F"No sites were left unmonitored during
OL,15,Fthis time, but the unique
OL,16,Fcircumstances of 2020/21 caused
OL,17,Fsignificant challenges and disruption
OL,18,Fto our operations."
